WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.040 --> 01:40.280
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.040 --> 01:48.840
Tie Ying commands an elite squad
of covert warfare.

01:49.560 --> 01:50.960
Night raid on Wuyang Pass,

01:51.040 --> 01:52.280
fire on Panying Pass,

01:52.360 --> 01:53.520
and massacre at Qingshi Stronghold.

01:54.360 --> 01:55.800
They've never failed.

01:57.200 --> 01:59.320
I've heard about this squad.

01:59.840 --> 02:03.000
They always strike on dark, windy nights,

02:03.080 --> 02:04.560
slaying all who stand in their way.

02:05.280 --> 02:07.040
In that case,

02:07.640 --> 02:09.919
I don't think we're likely to win.

02:13.960 --> 02:14.800
Not really.

02:14.880 --> 02:19.440
This squad excels at night raids
because they have superb hearing.

02:20.200 --> 02:22.440
That's why they can move freely
in the darkness.

02:25.000 --> 02:26.640
There's a way.

02:26.720 --> 02:28.680
We can set traps in the bamboo forest

02:29.280 --> 02:30.280
and catch them off guard.

02:30.960 --> 02:32.760
Then we'll shoot them from the shadows.

02:33.880 --> 02:37.040
Then, we might stand a chance.

02:41.360 --> 02:43.360
The whistle is our code.

02:43.440 --> 02:44.320
You can use it

02:44.400 --> 02:46.920
to make our people to set traps for you.

02:47.000 --> 02:49.480
During the fight, use it to communicate.

02:51.040 --> 02:51.960
Thank you.

02:52.560 --> 02:53.800
Tie Ying is mine.

03:17.320 --> 03:19.080
Mere child's play.

05:05.640 --> 05:08.320
Jiu, when you kill, you have steady hands.

05:09.360 --> 05:10.800
But now, they shake.

05:13.240 --> 05:14.200
I failed to protect you.

05:15.080 --> 05:16.040
Don't mind.

05:16.640 --> 05:17.680
It matters to me.

05:20.240 --> 05:22.960
Before, it was an order.

05:24.240 --> 05:25.200
But now,

05:26.800 --> 05:27.720
it's my duty.

05:30.160 --> 05:31.000
And the future?

05:34.320 --> 05:35.280
In the future…

05:41.200 --> 05:42.240
We'll see.

05:47.480 --> 05:48.400
Whatever happens,

05:49.240 --> 05:50.760
I will protect you.

05:58.880 --> 05:59.720
Tie Ying retreated.

05:59.800 --> 06:01.360
Your father is safe now.

06:04.520 --> 06:05.680
Thank you, ma'am.

06:12.080 --> 06:13.280
You helped a lot.

06:13.360 --> 06:16.840
To protect me, you suffered heavy losses.

06:18.800 --> 06:20.240
I don't know

06:21.240 --> 06:22.560
how I can repay you.

06:23.840 --> 06:25.760
Since we promised to protect you,

06:25.840 --> 06:27.680
we will keep our word.

06:28.280 --> 06:29.240
Tie Ying retreated.

06:29.320 --> 06:32.040
But more troops will be sent from Xiaonan.

06:33.920 --> 06:35.400
You'd better leave soon.

06:36.920 --> 06:37.800
Wait.

06:42.080 --> 06:43.560
My father gave this to me.

06:44.080 --> 06:46.560
When this is all over
and I'm back in the Capital,

06:46.640 --> 06:50.000
you people can ask me for rewards
with this jade pendant.

06:50.080 --> 06:51.840
‎WAR ENDS

06:57.560 --> 06:58.400
All right.

07:09.280 --> 07:11.160
What a nice piece of jade.

07:19.960 --> 07:21.520
Come on. Take it.

07:29.520 --> 07:30.800
Eat some of this.

07:38.320 --> 07:39.560
Have you noticed

07:40.480 --> 07:43.000
the way she looks at you is a bit strange?

07:43.680 --> 07:44.720
She means no harm.

07:46.200 --> 07:47.400
But strange, indeed.

07:51.160 --> 07:53.440
I think Tie Ying has fled back to Xiaonan.

07:54.200 --> 07:56.000
Xiao Xun's men will come again.

07:56.080 --> 07:57.360
It's not wise to stay here long.

07:57.440 --> 07:58.560
Right.

07:59.320 --> 08:00.520
We'll leave soon.

08:06.800 --> 08:10.800
Ma'am, in that fight, we had three dead
and seven badly injured.

08:10.880 --> 08:13.080
Three traps east were ruined
and need to be reset.

08:13.960 --> 08:15.480
Have our men properly settled.

08:15.560 --> 08:17.480
Yes. I'm on it.

08:17.560 --> 08:18.440
Let's go.

08:28.240 --> 08:29.440
You're about to leave?

08:31.520 --> 08:33.320
Don't bother to say goodbye.

08:33.400 --> 08:34.559
And you have apologized.

08:35.159 --> 08:37.120
But I have one question.

08:38.520 --> 08:42.400
What exactly happened
during my father's suppression?

08:44.320 --> 08:45.520
I told you, didn't I?

08:45.600 --> 08:46.520
I doubt it.

08:47.040 --> 08:48.200
I want the truth.

08:49.520 --> 08:52.080
This stronghold
is totally my father's style.

08:53.080 --> 08:55.520
I don't believe
it was just a misunderstanding.

08:56.280 --> 08:59.440
In that case, why did Mu Mianhong

09:00.040 --> 09:01.840
jump off a cliff instead of explaining?

09:09.960 --> 09:11.200
If you don't tell me,

09:12.480 --> 09:15.240
I might as well go ask my father.

09:22.000 --> 09:23.480
Do you know your father well?

09:24.120 --> 09:25.080
What kind of man

09:27.760 --> 09:29.120
do you think he is?

09:37.480 --> 09:38.560
My father…

09:40.280 --> 09:41.800
He's the God of War of our state

09:43.240 --> 09:45.160
and an all-powerful frontier hero.

09:46.200 --> 09:47.560
People respect him

09:48.520 --> 09:49.360
and revere him.

09:49.440 --> 09:50.520
Does that include you?

09:57.120 --> 09:58.560
Do you like this kind of father?

10:01.960 --> 10:02.920
No?

10:04.440 --> 10:05.280
Why?

10:12.120 --> 10:13.880
Because he's a hero to others.

10:16.280 --> 10:18.360
He's a hero to people in Yunzhong.

10:19.120 --> 10:20.440
He's a hero to the State of Chu.

10:21.640 --> 10:24.960
But I want him to be an ordinary father.

10:25.560 --> 10:27.200
Carve wooden dolls for me,

10:28.040 --> 10:29.720
watch fireworks with me,

10:31.120 --> 10:33.120
give me pretty braids,

10:34.840 --> 10:38.280
and be there with me
for every important moment.

10:41.000 --> 10:42.160
But actually…

10:44.080 --> 10:45.320
none of this happened.

10:47.600 --> 10:48.560
What about…

10:51.840 --> 10:52.800
your mother?

10:53.400 --> 10:54.400
My mother?

11:00.720 --> 11:02.680
I guess she's a great lady.

11:03.600 --> 11:05.120
According to my father,

11:05.760 --> 11:08.040
she's a perfect woman.

11:08.640 --> 11:09.880
She was well-learned

11:10.480 --> 11:12.480
and versed in all arts.

11:15.120 --> 11:16.720
Sadly, I didn't witness that.

11:18.960 --> 11:20.400
My mother died at a young age.

11:22.080 --> 11:26.480
For as long as I can remember,
I have no memories of her.

11:27.840 --> 11:29.200
Sometimes I wish,

11:30.960 --> 11:32.880
if only my mother were alive.

11:33.480 --> 11:36.520
Then she would have stood up for me
when Father scolded me.

11:37.360 --> 11:39.280
She would do my hair nicely.

11:39.360 --> 11:42.560
When people laughed at me
for failing at everything,

11:44.200 --> 11:45.840
she would still treasure me

11:47.080 --> 11:48.680
and always protect me.

11:50.920 --> 11:52.400
But what a pity.

11:52.480 --> 11:53.760
My mother is gone.

11:54.680 --> 11:56.600
Sometimes, I blame myself.

11:58.080 --> 12:01.760
Why couldn't I remember everything
when I was born?

12:02.760 --> 12:04.000
In that case,

12:05.400 --> 12:07.760
I would know what my mother looked like.

12:12.600 --> 12:15.360
My father claimed he loved my mother.

12:16.160 --> 12:17.720
But throughout our mansion,

12:18.520 --> 12:20.000
in the past 19 years,

12:20.080 --> 12:22.560
there has never been
a single portrait of her.

12:24.640 --> 12:26.000
In your imagination,

12:28.160 --> 12:29.800
what does she look like?

12:33.160 --> 12:35.160
She's a noble lady,
according to my father.

12:36.680 --> 12:37.960
So she must have

12:38.840 --> 12:40.360
delicate eyebrows,

12:41.320 --> 12:42.760
bright eyes,

12:44.840 --> 12:46.480
and porcelain skin.

12:53.840 --> 12:54.840
Girl,

12:56.680 --> 12:58.400
whatever your mother looks like,

13:02.120 --> 13:03.400
your father loves you

13:04.600 --> 13:06.120
more than his own life.

13:07.960 --> 13:09.560
This has never changed.

13:20.040 --> 13:21.400
Zhao.

13:22.400 --> 13:24.080
How could you not know

13:24.160 --> 13:25.600
your letter

13:26.480 --> 13:30.680
would make him let down his guard?

13:31.760 --> 13:32.720
You're right.

13:38.000 --> 13:39.400
And that's enough.

13:51.480 --> 13:52.720
Your mother loves you too.

14:22.920 --> 14:25.040
Sorry, I failed.

14:25.120 --> 14:26.360
Please forgive me.

14:29.640 --> 14:30.680
Where are our men?

14:32.280 --> 14:33.400
The terrain there is eerie.

14:34.000 --> 14:35.560
Too many traps in the forest.

14:35.640 --> 14:38.520
We lost over half of our men.

14:40.640 --> 14:42.360
But I've figured out their defenses.

14:42.440 --> 14:43.560
I request another attack.

14:44.240 --> 14:47.040
Chu Zhao isn't stupid enough
to wait there to die.

14:47.680 --> 14:49.480
She's eager to go back to Yunzhong.

14:49.560 --> 14:51.400
She won't stay long there.

14:52.000 --> 14:55.360
She has to pass through Wangcheng
to get to Yunzhong.

14:55.960 --> 14:58.240
Since Cangmu Stronghold
is tough to invade,

15:00.280 --> 15:01.920
we'll be waiting for her further ahead.

15:02.920 --> 15:05.080
Cangmu Stronghold lies at a key junction.

15:05.160 --> 15:06.720
If Chu Ling incorporates them,

15:07.280 --> 15:08.920
he will be more formidable.

15:11.920 --> 15:12.960
Tie Ying,

15:14.040 --> 15:15.280
send word to the Northern Desert.

15:16.520 --> 15:20.680
Tell them I want another deal
with their king.

15:28.040 --> 15:30.040
Congratulations. You won again.

15:35.520 --> 15:36.400
Do you think

15:37.480 --> 15:40.680
Zhao will be in trouble?

15:41.280 --> 15:42.440
Don't worry. Your Majesty.

15:42.520 --> 15:44.520
Before Her Highness left,
I divined for her.

15:44.600 --> 15:47.640
During the trip,
she'll escape all misfortune.

15:49.800 --> 15:50.720
Your Majesty.

15:55.400 --> 15:57.600
Uncle, did you come so late

15:57.680 --> 16:00.120
because Zhao and Uncle Yanlai
were in some trouble?

16:01.720 --> 16:03.640
Yanlai is skilled in martial arts.

16:03.720 --> 16:05.160
He'll protect Zhao.

16:05.240 --> 16:06.560
Don't worry.

16:06.640 --> 16:08.320
General Chu Ling

16:08.400 --> 16:10.640
killed the envoy without permission.

16:11.160 --> 16:12.480
It might lead to trouble.

16:13.080 --> 16:14.680
His old illness relapsed too.

16:14.760 --> 16:16.240
He might not survive this winter.

16:17.240 --> 16:20.120
In the court, the Grand Mentor said,

16:20.720 --> 16:23.800
if General Chu died, war would break out.

16:24.400 --> 16:26.920
So, our frontier forces
should prepare early.

16:27.520 --> 16:28.480
Exactly.

16:29.400 --> 16:32.720
The 200,000 frontier troops in Yunzhong
safeguard our state.

16:33.320 --> 16:35.200
If Northern Desert foes invade…

16:35.280 --> 16:36.200
Yu,

16:37.200 --> 16:38.560
do you dare to fight in battle?

16:39.360 --> 16:40.880
I will fight.

16:41.400 --> 16:43.200
We people never fear a battle.

16:44.640 --> 16:45.560
Good.

16:46.080 --> 16:49.320
Let me ask you one more thing.

16:49.920 --> 16:51.080
If Chu Ling dies,

16:51.600 --> 16:55.600
who should command
the 200,000 frontier troops?

16:57.320 --> 16:59.360
Uncle Yanlai. He has great martial arts.

17:06.280 --> 17:07.200
Your Majesty,

17:07.280 --> 17:09.319
then get the edict ready.

17:09.400 --> 17:10.599
So we can plan ahead.

17:12.800 --> 17:13.920
Wait, Your Majesty.

17:18.839 --> 17:20.880
Mr. Xie, you're really impatient.

17:23.079 --> 17:26.560
Your Majesty,
military affairs are of vital importance

17:27.160 --> 17:28.280
and need court discussion.

17:29.120 --> 17:31.120
Mr. Xie shouldn't have incited you
in private.

17:31.200 --> 17:34.840
Mr. Deng,
are you trying to delay military action?

17:35.480 --> 17:36.840
I hold the Imperial Seal.

17:36.920 --> 17:39.840
Without the seal on it,
this edict will be invalid.

17:41.040 --> 17:43.040
The Three Departments
approve troop deployment.

17:43.640 --> 17:47.800
It's time for you to end
this practice of nepotism.

18:03.680 --> 18:06.360
‎MILITARY CAMP OF NORTHERN DESERT

18:14.600 --> 18:15.720
Word from Xiao Xun.

18:15.800 --> 18:17.120
Chu Ling is seriously sick.

18:17.200 --> 18:18.320
The Chu court is in chaos.

18:18.920 --> 18:21.320
He wants 3,000 elite soldiers of ours

18:21.400 --> 18:23.720
to bypass Xiaonan and go to Wangcheng

18:24.240 --> 18:26.080
to join the Xiaonan Army
in besieging Yunzhong.

18:26.160 --> 18:29.640
Then, we'll split his state.

18:31.360 --> 18:33.520
He's the most eager of all.

18:34.120 --> 18:36.120
After all these years as a hostage,

18:36.200 --> 18:38.920
he still hasn't become patient.

18:39.520 --> 18:41.320
Come on, Chu Ling.

18:42.720 --> 18:45.480
We've been fighting for two decades.

18:45.560 --> 18:48.720
The state you've guarded with your life

18:49.320 --> 18:51.520
corroded from within a long time ago.

18:57.360 --> 18:58.880
Their ministers scheme against each other.

18:58.960 --> 18:59.800
KING OF NORTHERN DESERT

18:59.880 --> 19:01.240
Even a hostage dares

19:02.920 --> 19:05.760
to collude with enemies for invasion.

19:09.880 --> 19:15.080
Now, it's our time to take over Yunzhong.

19:15.960 --> 19:18.520
But mountain defiles
are perilous in Xiaonan.

19:18.600 --> 19:20.120
Supplies can't get through.

19:20.720 --> 19:24.000
Wangcheng lies to the rear of Yunzhong.

19:25.600 --> 19:27.600
It's weakly guarded.

19:28.320 --> 19:31.720
We'll travel light for a night raid.

19:31.800 --> 19:34.120
Capturing it quickly won't be a problem.

19:39.200 --> 19:41.320
Go. Tell Xiao Xun.

19:41.400 --> 19:44.680
I will wait for him in Wangcheng.

19:49.880 --> 19:52.480
WANGCHENG

19:57.600 --> 20:01.160
Son, we need to think carefully.

20:02.760 --> 20:05.120
The Northern Desert King is treacherous.

20:05.200 --> 20:08.280
To work with him is to play with fire.

20:08.960 --> 20:11.080
He has probed me for years,

20:11.160 --> 20:12.320
but I've never agreed.

20:12.400 --> 20:15.360
If we work with him,
there may be unnecessary trouble.

20:17.280 --> 20:18.760
Can you guarantee

20:19.800 --> 20:22.040
that everything will be under control

20:22.120 --> 20:24.360
once his soldiers come in here?

20:26.520 --> 20:28.480
Without a perfect plan,

20:31.880 --> 20:33.520
we might as well wait.

20:34.840 --> 20:36.600
Father, I understand your concern.

20:37.320 --> 20:38.520
But in some cases,

20:39.840 --> 20:41.480
patience doesn't solve anything.

20:42.360 --> 20:44.840
I don't want to repeat the same mistakes.

20:46.640 --> 20:47.840
Chu Ling is badly ill.

20:48.680 --> 20:50.400
This is the perfect moment.

20:51.000 --> 20:52.320
We'll use our northern foes

20:53.200 --> 20:54.800
to support our own cause.

21:02.320 --> 21:03.840
I get it.

21:03.920 --> 21:06.040
Since you've made up your mind,

21:07.640 --> 21:08.520
go ahead and do it.

21:10.800 --> 21:12.120
Thank you, Father.

21:14.680 --> 21:17.760
I should send a few men to escort you.

21:19.040 --> 21:21.080
I've brought too much trouble to you.

21:21.160 --> 21:22.600
Many innocent people died.

21:23.480 --> 21:25.760
I will keep that in mind.

21:29.040 --> 21:30.160
You helped us at all costs.

21:30.760 --> 21:32.960
Whatever you want, just let me know.

21:34.240 --> 21:35.640
We want nothing from you.

21:36.720 --> 21:38.600
We just hope you won't forget us

21:38.680 --> 21:41.320
when you're back there
and grant us some rewards.

21:41.960 --> 21:43.040
I will.

21:45.000 --> 21:46.360
That jade piece…

21:46.440 --> 21:47.640
Please keep it for me.

21:48.360 --> 21:49.520
Sure.

21:50.240 --> 21:52.800
Cangmu Forest isn't far from Wangcheng.

21:52.880 --> 21:55.320
Xiaonan's killers may pursue you, though.

21:55.960 --> 21:57.600
Every half day, Wangcheng soldiers

21:57.680 --> 21:59.640
patrol the foot of the mountain.

22:00.560 --> 22:01.600
Be more careful out there.

22:03.160 --> 22:04.760
Thank you for reminding me.

22:04.840 --> 22:05.880
We know what to do.

22:07.160 --> 22:08.000
That's good.

22:13.000 --> 22:14.200
Take care.

22:18.320 --> 22:22.240
‎GATEWAY OF CANGMU STRONGHOLD

22:42.520 --> 22:44.880
IN HARMONY WITH YIN AND YANG

22:47.840 --> 22:50.840
You issued the transfer edict, right?

22:53.920 --> 22:56.360
Where did you get this?

22:56.880 --> 23:00.560
Theoretically,
this edict should have left the Capital.

23:01.280 --> 23:04.920
Intercepting an imperial edict
is a grave crime.

23:05.520 --> 23:06.640
I did intercept it.

23:11.600 --> 23:13.240
What does it mean?

23:17.440 --> 23:18.400
It means

23:18.960 --> 23:20.880
without my approval,

23:21.920 --> 23:23.680
it can't be issued.

23:23.760 --> 23:28.080
Do you think I can't hold you accountable
just because of who you are?

23:28.160 --> 23:29.480
You can do that.

23:30.400 --> 23:32.040
But I advise you not to do that.

23:32.680 --> 23:34.440
If we both lose in the end,

23:35.400 --> 23:36.760
our state will be in peril.

23:36.840 --> 23:39.920
Since you know that,
why don't you advise yourself?

23:40.520 --> 23:44.160
You don't fear the peril of the state.
Why would I be scared?

23:44.760 --> 23:47.800
So late at night, you visited
His Majesty and coaxed him.

23:47.880 --> 23:49.840
Why can't I ease his burdens?

23:49.920 --> 23:51.520
Of course, you aren't afraid.

23:52.120 --> 23:56.400
But the way you ease burdens
is a clear overreach of your authority.

23:57.360 --> 24:00.880
How dare you issue an edict
without His Majesty's decision?

24:01.680 --> 24:03.320
Do you also want

24:04.160 --> 24:05.840
to sit on the throne

24:06.440 --> 24:07.920
to ease His Majesty's burdens?

24:09.040 --> 24:11.480
You overestimate me, Mr. Xie.

24:12.040 --> 24:14.560
His Majesty is aware of all this.

24:15.320 --> 24:16.320
As for you…

24:16.400 --> 24:19.160
Do you really think
Chu Ling's defeat of an enemy army

24:19.240 --> 24:21.040
will bring peace?

24:22.000 --> 24:23.680
Once Chu Ling dies a sudden death,

24:23.760 --> 24:26.160
Yunzhong troops will fall into chaos.

24:26.680 --> 24:28.960
Then our state will be in real peril.

24:29.920 --> 24:31.000
Others might not know.

24:31.080 --> 24:32.400
But we both know

24:32.480 --> 24:36.440
what the Lord of Xiaonan will do
when Yunzhong is in chaos.

24:36.520 --> 24:38.600
What will the Lord of Xiaonan do?

24:40.800 --> 24:42.560
You know it perfectly well, don't you?

24:43.600 --> 24:46.760
Back then, you insisted
Xiao Xun return to Xiaonan.

24:47.360 --> 24:48.720
When the hostage left,

24:48.800 --> 24:50.640
you should have foreseen this day.

24:50.720 --> 24:52.280
Xie Yanfang!

24:53.400 --> 24:56.280
Your duty is merely to enforce edicts.

24:56.360 --> 24:58.480
You have no say in military affairs.

24:58.560 --> 25:00.120
This is a real overreach of authority!

25:01.760 --> 25:06.480
WISDOM AND VIRTUES

25:14.600 --> 25:16.440
Here's the Grand Princess Token.

25:17.480 --> 25:21.080
I'm exercising the veto power
on behalf of Her Highness.

25:26.360 --> 25:28.280
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

25:36.680 --> 25:37.520
Madam Ge said,

25:37.600 --> 25:40.200
Wangcheng soldiers patrol at this hour.

25:40.280 --> 25:41.600
She's right.

25:42.960 --> 25:46.720
So, what exactly is your great plan?

25:47.360 --> 25:48.720
We'll "surrender".

25:51.000 --> 25:55.240
Are you saying we'll deliberately
let these patrols catch us

25:55.320 --> 25:56.160
and take us to Wangcheng?

25:56.880 --> 26:00.280
So, Mr. Xie, show some mercy in the fight.

26:02.440 --> 26:03.360
Who are you?

26:05.800 --> 26:06.840
I don't think

26:07.840 --> 26:09.120
there'll be a fight.

26:13.160 --> 26:14.480
<i>It's him.</i>

26:19.120 --> 26:20.360
<i>In my past life,</i>

26:20.880 --> 26:23.320
<i>he was a vanguard</i>
<i>under my father's command.</i>

26:23.400 --> 26:25.640
<i>But now, he seems to be</i>

26:26.520 --> 26:29.280
<i>a foot soldier among Wangcheng troops.</i>

26:30.280 --> 26:31.120
Liang Qiang.

26:35.120 --> 26:36.600
How do you know my name?

26:36.680 --> 26:39.680
Mr. Xie, you don't allow me
to dispatch new generals.

26:40.560 --> 26:42.320
And you seem to have decent excuses.

26:43.160 --> 26:45.840
Actually, it's just because
they are not loyal to you.

26:46.440 --> 26:47.640
Then do you think

26:48.560 --> 26:52.600
you can plant your own men
after you stop me?

26:53.200 --> 26:54.840
You don't trust me.

26:56.280 --> 26:58.000
I don't trust you either.

26:59.040 --> 27:00.880
So we should place our trust in Chu Ling.

27:01.920 --> 27:04.560
We must believe he will handle
everything before he dies.

27:05.240 --> 27:06.560
Chaos won't occur.

27:07.080 --> 27:09.320
Northern Desert foes won't invade.

27:11.040 --> 27:14.120
Once our state is in crisis,
we'll be in danger.

27:14.720 --> 27:16.200
So will Chu Ling.

27:17.040 --> 27:18.040
If our state falls,

27:18.120 --> 27:20.800
as the Grand Princess,
her daughter will die too.

27:20.880 --> 27:25.480
Chu Ling won't let her daughter
fall into danger.

27:30.560 --> 27:31.440
Fine.

27:33.080 --> 27:36.040
Since the generals can't go to Yunzhong,

27:36.920 --> 27:38.080
Mr. Xie,

27:40.720 --> 27:45.240
your private troops must not go there too.

27:51.600 --> 27:54.920
I read the files on your father's
connection to the Third Prince.

27:59.160 --> 28:00.080
Who are you?

28:02.560 --> 28:03.920
The Third Prince was executed.

28:04.000 --> 28:05.200
His subordinates were demoted.

28:05.960 --> 28:07.440
Your family collapsed.

28:07.520 --> 28:09.560
You became a patrol soldier then.

28:09.640 --> 28:12.360
Would you really waste your life
in the middle of nowhere?

28:14.200 --> 28:16.480
-Who on earth are you?
-I'm here to help.

28:17.840 --> 28:18.800
We're merely bandits

28:18.880 --> 28:20.880
who have fled from Cangmu Stronghold.

28:21.800 --> 28:24.200
You patrolled here and ran into bandits.

28:24.280 --> 28:27.000
If you take us back,
you'll make great merit.

28:27.080 --> 28:28.760
We just switched allegiance.

28:28.840 --> 28:30.120
Don't be suspicious.

28:30.720 --> 28:35.600
You just need to decide
whether you want that credit.

28:36.480 --> 28:39.480
Back in Wangcheng,
if you dare to play tricks,

28:40.000 --> 28:41.040
I'll kill you immediately.

28:41.120 --> 28:43.600
Since you accept this merit,

28:43.680 --> 28:46.160
we will behave ourselves.

28:49.560 --> 28:51.360
CHARTING THE COSMOS

28:51.440 --> 28:52.280
Mr. Xie,

28:54.760 --> 28:59.120
where is your brother
planning to take the Grand Princess?

29:03.520 --> 29:05.600
My brother has been suspended.

29:06.200 --> 29:07.640
Her Highness is recuperating.

29:08.240 --> 29:09.680
I don't know what you mean.

29:10.360 --> 29:12.080
Then let me remind you.

29:12.800 --> 29:15.400
He who holds the emperor
commands the lords.

29:15.480 --> 29:17.120
But he who holds the Grand Princess

29:17.760 --> 29:20.160
only commands Chu Ling.

29:20.240 --> 29:22.880
It's a bad bargain.
You know that perfectly well.

29:22.960 --> 29:25.040
Then you should also know.

29:26.640 --> 29:28.480
Chu Zhao must not die.

29:29.280 --> 29:31.520
She must stay alive.

29:31.600 --> 29:35.880
Only when she's alive
will the court avoid another rebellion.

29:36.400 --> 29:40.320
Then our game can keep going, right?

29:41.040 --> 29:42.400
In that case,

29:43.080 --> 29:45.640
hope your ninth brother
will protect Her Highness well

29:47.160 --> 29:49.720
as we all expect him to.

29:53.240 --> 29:55.040
Of course.

29:58.440 --> 30:00.560
But you're wrong about one thing.

30:02.400 --> 30:04.680
My brother didn't take away
the Grand Princess.

30:05.280 --> 30:08.800
Instead, the Grand Princess
took away my brother.

30:11.520 --> 30:15.400
CHARTING THE COSMOS

30:16.560 --> 30:18.360
Mr. Deng, you're pretty bold.

30:22.040 --> 30:24.960
You removed the coffin
bestowed by Her Highness.

30:25.920 --> 30:28.520
Her Highness withdrew from the court.

30:28.600 --> 30:30.120
Why can't I move this little thing then?

30:44.360 --> 30:45.640
Impressive.

30:45.720 --> 30:46.640
Let me try.

30:53.320 --> 30:55.320
Hello, Miss Qi. Hello, Lady Tang.

31:01.880 --> 31:03.560
That totally ruined my mood.

31:04.360 --> 31:05.560
What are you talking about?

31:05.640 --> 31:06.680
What did we do?

31:06.760 --> 31:09.920
Is it because we didn't bow
to Miss Chu Tang?

31:10.600 --> 31:11.920
You should be straightforward.

31:12.520 --> 31:14.440
Why do you bother to be so sarcastic?

31:15.040 --> 31:16.080
All right.

31:18.760 --> 31:21.600
Lady Tang, let me ask you.

31:21.680 --> 31:25.600
Do you know if your uncle General Chu Ling
fails to defend the frontier,

31:25.680 --> 31:27.720
people will suffer?

31:32.000 --> 31:33.360
I know.

31:33.440 --> 31:34.600
You speak recklessly

31:35.200 --> 31:37.280
because you worry
about our state and people.

31:37.360 --> 31:38.440
This is good.

31:38.960 --> 31:41.240
Unmarried ladies like us
should pay more attention

31:41.320 --> 31:42.440
to state affairs.

31:42.520 --> 31:46.040
Only then will we know about the hardships
of our state and people.

31:46.720 --> 31:49.120
However, we must not judge by appearances

31:49.200 --> 31:51.280
or take a part for the whole.

31:51.360 --> 31:53.080
We didn't speak recklessly.

31:53.160 --> 31:55.040
What we said is the truth.

31:55.120 --> 31:56.760
What is truth? What you see is truth.

31:56.840 --> 31:58.160
Did you see with your own eyes

31:58.240 --> 32:01.320
that my uncle failed
and our foes gained an advantage?

32:01.920 --> 32:02.960
Don't try to deny it.

32:06.080 --> 32:07.640
Do you know how big Yunzhong is?

32:07.720 --> 32:10.200
Do you know how many soldiers
are involved in a battle?

32:10.280 --> 32:13.400
Do you know how many people
from the Northern Desert

32:13.480 --> 32:16.760
have come to travel
on the trade routes of our state?

32:17.480 --> 32:22.280
When the case is investigated,
my uncle will be convicted or vindicated.

32:22.880 --> 32:26.200
But now,
no one can convict him without proof.

32:28.360 --> 32:31.760
Once war breaks out,
situations are volatile and intricate.

32:32.280 --> 32:34.800
Even the Emperor's orders
aren't always followed.

32:35.560 --> 32:38.840
And you don't even know
what exactly happened in Yunzhong.

32:38.920 --> 32:40.280
How can you parrot what others say?

32:41.280 --> 32:42.200
Let's go.

32:44.360 --> 32:45.200
LOTUS PAVILION

32:45.280 --> 32:46.320
Come on.

32:47.600 --> 32:48.440
Tang.

32:49.080 --> 32:50.120
I…

32:55.040 --> 32:56.280
I'm sorry.

32:56.360 --> 32:58.120
Miss Chu, you seem to be in good spirits.

32:59.280 --> 33:01.280
Your family is in turmoil.

33:01.360 --> 33:02.440
But you're in the mood for tea.

33:03.600 --> 33:06.040
If you're here for some fun, get in there.

33:06.120 --> 33:07.400
More fun with the storyteller.

33:08.000 --> 33:10.040
Tang, how can you be so rude to Mr. Deng?

33:11.160 --> 33:12.520
He wanted to watch the fun,

33:12.600 --> 33:14.720
then I recommended the opera house.
How was that rude?

33:14.800 --> 33:16.960
Has my entire family
already been convicted

33:17.040 --> 33:18.080
that I can't even speak?

33:18.160 --> 33:19.160
You can speak.

33:19.760 --> 33:22.640
Lady Tang, your frankness
is quite admirable.

33:23.240 --> 33:24.880
Even if your uncle ends up guilty,

33:24.960 --> 33:26.640
the Grand Princess will stand by you.

33:28.760 --> 33:30.960
You've got a point there,
Mr. Deng. Farewell.

33:35.120 --> 33:36.920
Tang, wait for me.

33:43.160 --> 33:44.320
Oh no.

33:44.400 --> 33:46.600
What was I even saying?

33:46.680 --> 33:47.600
Yeah.

33:48.120 --> 33:49.280
Scared now, huh?

33:50.040 --> 33:51.760
What happened to all that swagger?

33:52.920 --> 33:55.160
Come on. Don't tease me.

33:55.240 --> 33:58.120
Just now, I lost my temper.

33:58.200 --> 34:00.520
I couldn't remember what I said or did.

34:02.400 --> 34:03.520
Now I've come to my senses.

34:05.200 --> 34:06.600
I'm so terrified.

34:11.920 --> 34:13.360
Anyway, what's gone is gone.

34:13.880 --> 34:16.920
Even if I said that,
who would dare to do anything?

34:17.880 --> 34:19.040
Tang,

34:20.360 --> 34:22.679
you've changed.

34:24.920 --> 34:26.600
You never argued with anyone before.

34:27.320 --> 34:29.480
Not to mention arguing
for General Chu and Chu Zhao.

34:34.080 --> 34:35.560
Oh, my uncle.

34:36.280 --> 34:37.960
Please don't get convicted.

34:39.360 --> 34:40.400
And Zhao…

34:40.480 --> 34:42.159
Come back early.

34:42.760 --> 34:45.159
‎WANGCHENG OUTSKIRTS

34:50.120 --> 34:54.199
Before fully recovering,
you exhausted yourself again.

34:54.719 --> 34:55.719
I know what I'm doing.

34:59.280 --> 35:00.360
Can we trust this man?

35:00.960 --> 35:04.480
Liang Qiang is low-ranking,
but he's a regular soldier.

35:04.560 --> 35:07.000
Xiao Xun's troops
won't provoke or inspect him.

35:07.640 --> 35:10.800
In this way,
we'll be able to avoid Xiao Xun's spies.

35:11.400 --> 35:14.320
Besides, we're taking a carriage now.

35:14.400 --> 35:16.240
No soft cushions or pillows.

35:16.320 --> 35:18.960
But at least, we don't need to trek.

35:19.040 --> 35:20.960
How nice. Two birds, one stone.

35:24.920 --> 35:29.760
WANGCHENG

35:37.120 --> 35:38.040
Get them down.

36:07.520 --> 36:08.560
The ruts are weird.

36:09.160 --> 36:11.040
It seems to be a straw cart
heading for town.

36:13.240 --> 36:14.800
The straw binding is loose.

36:15.800 --> 36:17.080
Usually, a loosely bound cart bears

36:17.680 --> 36:20.000
no more than three to five hundred jin.

36:20.080 --> 36:22.480
But the ruts are deeper
than half a finger.

36:22.560 --> 36:23.960
It carries at least

36:25.200 --> 36:26.400
800 jin.

36:26.480 --> 36:27.920
There's something else in the cart.

36:31.600 --> 36:32.760
Judging from the ruts,

36:32.840 --> 36:36.680
no fewer than ten carts
have entered town today.

36:37.360 --> 36:40.920
Someone's taking so much trouble
to do something to this town.

36:41.520 --> 36:43.120
This is a strategic frontier town.

36:43.640 --> 36:48.040
If it falls, Yunzhong Prefecture
will be attacked from the front and rear.

36:49.680 --> 36:51.720
Xiao Xun sent his men in disguise.

36:52.560 --> 36:54.920
But the gate guards should have inspected

36:55.000 --> 36:56.880
either disguised men or hidden weapons.

36:56.960 --> 36:58.400
By Article ten of the Frontier Code,

36:59.040 --> 37:02.760
a Military Supply Token will exempt
all goods from inspection.

37:03.600 --> 37:05.840
Given Xiao Xun's status,
getting some tokens

37:06.840 --> 37:07.840
would be quite easy.

37:09.560 --> 37:10.400
Follow me in.

37:11.560 --> 37:12.640
You go back now.

37:14.240 --> 37:15.520
Keep up.

37:21.560 --> 37:22.720
Your Highness,

37:22.800 --> 37:25.080
3,000 elite troops of Northern Desert
passed Xinggu Pass

37:25.160 --> 37:26.800
and reached Shalang Col,
less than 100 li from Wangcheng.

37:28.840 --> 37:30.560
Tell them to go along the official road

37:31.800 --> 37:33.720
with the travel permit,
disguised as caravans.

37:34.360 --> 37:37.520
-Make sure they're well provisioned.
-Yes.

37:38.120 --> 37:40.000
We won't dispatch troops

37:41.200 --> 37:42.520
until they take Wangcheng.

37:44.560 --> 37:47.000
Ge. Ge. Bad news.

37:48.040 --> 37:51.000
Our scout spotted
3,000 soldiers headed for Wangcheng

37:51.080 --> 37:52.840
from the official road northwest
toward Xiaonan,

37:52.920 --> 37:54.400
disguised as caravans.

37:54.480 --> 37:55.960
From Xiaonan?

37:57.320 --> 37:59.720
Wangcheng is vital
to the rear of Yunzhong.

38:00.240 --> 38:01.600
Once it falls,

38:01.680 --> 38:04.400
Xiao Xun will block supplies
within half a day.

38:05.240 --> 38:09.400
By then, the Yunzhong troops
will be besieged with no supplies.

38:10.000 --> 38:12.840
Massive soldiers
will be desperately trapped.

38:14.560 --> 38:15.560
Oh no.

38:16.080 --> 38:17.760
At the rate of traveling,

38:18.680 --> 38:20.680
the two of them are just at Wangcheng.

38:20.760 --> 38:23.840
JUSTICE HANGS ON HIGH

38:23.920 --> 38:27.880
General, in Cangmu Forest, I caught
two bandits of Cangmu Stronghold.

38:28.400 --> 38:30.520
Bandits have done countless crimes.

38:30.600 --> 38:31.640
Execute them now.

38:33.440 --> 38:35.360
General, it's easy for you to kill us.

38:35.440 --> 38:38.080
But I wonder if you can remain so decisive

38:38.160 --> 38:40.040
when northern foes break into town.

38:46.160 --> 38:48.560
How dare you!

38:48.640 --> 38:50.440
How could you spread a fallacy here?

38:50.520 --> 38:53.360
If we were real bandits,
why would we come voluntarily?

38:54.360 --> 38:57.240
As we entered town,
we spotted enemy spies in disguise.

38:57.840 --> 39:00.280
The ruts of straw carts
are abnormally deep.

39:00.360 --> 39:01.360
Weapons must be hidden there.

39:02.040 --> 39:04.560
Now, instead of executing me,

39:04.640 --> 39:07.600
you should send men
to close the city gate,

39:07.680 --> 39:09.320
search the city, and increase security.

39:09.400 --> 39:10.360
Shut up!

39:13.120 --> 39:15.720
How dare a bandit
comment on military affairs,

39:15.800 --> 39:18.040
stir up unrest, and shake troop morale?

39:18.120 --> 39:20.120
I'll chop your heads off now

39:20.200 --> 39:22.320
and hang them
on the city wall as a warning!

39:22.400 --> 39:24.000
Kill them!

39:37.120 --> 39:38.240
Brilliant plan.

39:38.320 --> 39:40.080
Xiao Xun didn't kill you.

39:40.160 --> 39:42.120
But someone on your own side will.

39:42.200 --> 39:43.120
You're wrong.

39:43.640 --> 39:46.960
You've been the only one on my own side.

39:48.840 --> 39:50.400
Outrageous. Outrageous!

39:50.480 --> 39:53.040
Seize them immediately and execute them!

39:53.840 --> 39:54.680
Don't you dare!

40:02.600 --> 40:04.720
Zhong Changrong,
deputy of the Guard General,

40:04.800 --> 40:06.560
is here to see the Grand Princess!

40:43.600 --> 40:44.440
Hey, girl.

40:46.680 --> 40:47.520
Girl.

41:14.960 --> 41:15.920
Hey.

41:19.240 --> 41:20.120
Hey.

41:20.840 --> 41:21.920
It's been years.

41:22.560 --> 41:23.800
Don't you recognize me?

41:27.480 --> 41:28.400
Mr. Zhong.

41:29.040 --> 41:30.920
Did anyone bully you?

41:35.160 --> 41:36.000
You…

41:36.520 --> 41:38.680
You vile creature! Are you blind?

41:38.760 --> 41:41.640
This is General Chu's daughter,
the Grand Princess.

41:42.320 --> 41:43.520
Just now,

41:43.600 --> 41:45.880
who were you going to execute?

41:48.640 --> 41:50.160
Sorry, I misjudged you.

41:50.240 --> 41:51.640
Mercy, Your Highness.

41:53.640 --> 41:54.480
My eyes failed me,

41:55.080 --> 41:56.560
and I offended Your Highness.

41:56.640 --> 41:57.480
Please forgive me.

41:58.720 --> 41:59.720
Not your fault.

42:00.520 --> 42:03.440
Your priority is to close the city gate
and defend deep.

42:03.520 --> 42:05.920
Find out Northern Desert foes and weapons.

42:07.200 --> 42:09.080
I swear to hold the city.

42:10.480 --> 42:13.840
Mr. Zhao,
your official headwear is still yours now.

42:14.560 --> 42:19.000
But if this city falls,
you will lose it and your life.

42:19.600 --> 42:22.080
I swear to stand and fall with the city!

42:22.680 --> 42:24.720
Leave us right now. Get to work.

42:31.440 --> 42:33.320
Mr. Zhong, why are you here?

42:35.160 --> 42:36.560
Your father was worried about you,

42:36.640 --> 42:38.960
so he sent me here
to get you back to Yunzhong.

42:39.040 --> 42:40.760
When I was halfway,

42:40.840 --> 42:42.640
I got this man's message,

42:42.720 --> 42:44.760
saying you would reach Wangcheng.

42:45.360 --> 42:46.920
I traveled hundreds of li for nothing

42:47.000 --> 42:49.160
and rushed back immediately.

42:49.240 --> 42:50.800
You arrived later than I expected.

42:51.400 --> 42:54.040
Zhong, you should work on your speed.

42:55.160 --> 42:56.920
How rude. Nonsense.

42:58.840 --> 43:00.400
Report!

43:00.480 --> 43:01.560
‎THE WAY OF HEAVEN, THE JUSTICE OF ALL

43:01.640 --> 43:03.040
Scouts have spotted

43:03.120 --> 43:05.200
3,000 enemy troops came from the north.

43:05.280 --> 43:07.080
They're within 50 li of this city.
